Package org.lfj.lang.util

Class ReflectiveTypeDispatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.lfj.lang.util.TypeDispatcher
      • org.lfj.lang.util.ReflectiveTypeDispatcher
  • public class ReflectiveTypeDispatcher
extends TypeDispatcher
    This dispatches member specs based upon reflection upon a given class which has already been loaded. This can be achieved by using the java reflection library and going through the fields and methods defined by the class.
